{"tid":2307330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 銷售威力驚人　韓、日唱片總銷量已破一千萬！","createTime":"2020-12-01T06:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T09:52:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b896627a0bb43c0222155160ddc19b1b11402924","tid":2307330,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_65ea2f6a03a4d28120fb62694f60935f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-01/132015-887102.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_65ea2f6a03a4d28120fb62694f60935f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-01%2F132015-887102.png&h=15219288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每次回歸都寫下驚人銷量的 TWICE，早在去年便已連三年寫下破百萬年度銷量；如今她們出道以來的所有作品，也已賣出超過一千萬張！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTWICE 於 2015 年 10 月帶著首張韓語迷你專輯〈The Story Begins〉出道，至今五年來已經在韓國和日本各自發行了 15 張單曲、迷你專輯、正規專輯、改版專輯或精選輯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6d84d354d774ce90951b2b61d3a4aeff/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-01/132015-887107.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6d84d354d774ce90951b2b61d3a4aeff%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-01%2F132015-887107.jpeg&h=c4a57a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而合計這五年來在韓國和日本發行過的所有作品，TWICE 的累積唱片銷量已達到 100,029,242 張，再度證明了 TWICE 驚人的實力和火熱人氣。<br />\n<br />\n特別的是，不久前 TWICE 憑著最新主打歌 &ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo; 登上了告示牌國際單曲榜的冠軍寶座，昨天她們也閃電公開英語版音源，另外也在《The Late Show with Stephen Colbert》上帶來了韓語版的表演！<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment、CBS）"},{"pid":"7a6bdb13dc1e23c4e04b72c5d7affbeeb3412725","tid":2307330,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"世界第一 就在今天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e799b9e04dd0e863b15738dd8bb74841afca8e","tid":2307330,"uid":224479,